==友好城市==
阿尔贝维尔与德国城市[[溫嫩登|溫嫩登]]自1969年起互为友好城市关系<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.savoie-news.fr/albertville-le-50eme-anniversaire-du-jumelage-albertville-winnenden/|title=ALBERTVILLE : LE 50ÈME ANNIVERSAIRE DU JUMELAGE ALBERTVILLE/WINNENDEN|accessdate=2020-02-25|editor=savoie-news.fr|language=fr|publisher=savoie-news.fr|archive-date=2020-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200530010227/http://www.savoie-news.fr/albertville-le-50eme-anniversaire-du-jumelage-albertville-winnenden/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

